<item>
            <title>[PIG-2619] HBaseStorage constructs a Scan with cacheBlocks = false</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2619</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Per &amp;lt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://hbase.apache.org/book/mapreduce.example.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://hbase.apache.org/book/mapreduce.example.html&lt;/a&gt;&amp;gt;, Scan objects for map-reduce jobs should disable cache blocks.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    scan.setCacheBlocks(false);  // don&apos;t set to true for MR jobs&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue and the attached patch does so for Pig&apos;s HBaseStorage.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
